query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('coding-style',
'comparison',
'computer-science',
'date',
'db2',
'ejb',
'find',
'pyqt5',
'seaborn',
'sql-update',
'task-parallel-library',
'windows-10',
'xamarin');
